Before the Holdfast Gate~
The trail changes here, from the stony earth of the descent, into the
rich, sandy soil of the valley floor.  Across the field and through the
great gates it runs, disappearing beyond.  Large murder-holes mark the
gate to both sides and above.  Further evidence of battle is upon the
gates themselves, the ancient wood scarred by axe and fire, but for all
appearances sturdy enough.
